<!--Views/Home/About-->
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About WellUp</h1>

            <div class="card mb-5">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Our Story</h3>
                    <p>WellUp was founded in 2019 with a simple mission: to make clean and fresh water accessible to everyone. What started as a small operation has grown into a trusted water delivery service that serves thousands of households and businesses.</p>

                    <p>Our founders recognized the need for a reliable water delivery service that puts customer satisfaction and water quality at the forefront. Today, we continue to uphold these values in everything we do.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-5">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>At WellUp, we believe that access to clean water is essential for a healthy lifestyle. Our mission is to deliver high-quality water to your doorstep with convenience, reliability, and exceptional service.</p>

                    <p>We are committed to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Providing safe, clean, and great-tasting water</li>
                        <li>Offering convenient and timely delivery services</li>
                        <li>Maintaining transparent and fair pricing</li>
                        <li>Reducing our environmental footprint through sustainable practices</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-5">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Our Water Quality</h3>
                    <p>We take water quality seriously. Our water undergoes a rigorous purification process that includes:</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Multi-stage Filtration</strong> - Removes particulates and impurities</li>
                        <li><strong>Reverse Osmosis</strong> - Eliminates dissolved solids and contaminants</li>
                        <li><strong>UV Treatment</strong> - Destroys harmful microorganisms</li>
                        <li><strong>Ozonation</strong> - Enhances taste and extends shelf life</li>
                        <li><strong>Quality Testing</strong> - Regular laboratory tests ensure consistent quality</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>Our water meets and exceeds all safety standards set by regulatory authorities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Our Promise</h3>
                    <p>At WellUp, we promise to:</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>Deliver your order on time, every time</li>
                        <li>Provide responsive and helpful customer service</li>
                        <li>Listen to your feedback and continually improve our services</li>
                        <li>Maintain the highest standards of water quality</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>We're not just delivering water – we're delivering peace of mind and contributing to your health and well-being.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>